#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "\\textbf{Starting Units:}\n"
#| "\\begin{itemize}\n"
#| "  \\item A Pack of \\svgunit{bronze} units with the \\textit{lowest} Recruitment cost\n"
